About two and a half years into my journey,
about 10/11 sessions, and the universe put

00:04:55.780 --> 00:05:01.960
me into this situation where I could
experience nothing except from within feminine

00:05:01.960 --> 00:05:02.960
identity.

00:05:02.960 --> 00:05:04.270
A feminine identity.

00:05:04.270 --> 00:05:09.449
And it was a feminine form,
a womanly form that was the exact opposite

00:05:09.449 --> 00:05:15.320
of my own male, academic, intellectually oriented
form.

00:05:15.320 --> 00:05:20.800
And it was totally terrifying to experience
myself being me, but not being me within a

00:05:20.800 --> 00:05:23.240
framework that I'd ever known before.

00:05:23.240 --> 00:05:24.310
And it just snapped me.

00:05:24.310 --> 00:05:30.949
And so when I let go,
and I yielded, then I became hundreds,

00:05:30.949 --> 00:05:35.080
potentially thousands of women, and was given
a journey

00:05:35.080 --> 00:05:39.040
into the world of women under the arm of the
Great Mother.

00:05:39.040 --> 00:05:42.210
And it was an ecstatic experience,
a wonderful experience.

00:05:42.210 --> 00:05:45.270
In fact, when it opened,
I thought, 'What was I so afraid of?'

00:05:45.270 --> 00:05:47.550
'Why was I afraid of this?

00:05:47.550 --> 00:05:49.910
This is marvelous.'

00:05:49.910 --> 00:05:55.650
And what was the universe was doing was,
it was basically teaching me that where

00:05:55.650 --> 00:05:59.000
I was going, gender does not exist.

00:05:59.000 --> 00:06:03.009
So all gender, all roles based on gender and
any aspect of my

00:06:03.009 --> 00:06:06.890
historical personality had to be surrendered.

00:06:06.890 --> 00:06:11.820
If I were going to experience more intimately,
what is there in the universe.

00:06:11.820 --> 00:06:16.120
So I would ask you this on behalf of the men
and women watching this,

00:06:16.120 --> 00:06:23.000
what was the most either terrifying
