00:06:30.270 --> 00:06:33.000
It was a reality, but it wasn't my reality.

00:06:33.000 --> 00:06:34.500
And I couldn't get out of it.

00:06:34.500 --> 00:06:38.410
I was trapped within a
feminine mode of experience that just wasn't

00:06:38.410 --> 00:06:39.720
me.

00:06:39.720 --> 00:06:43.410
There was nothing inherently frightening about
it.

00:06:43.410 --> 00:06:50.110
And then when I let go and flowed with that
experience, oh, what a- it was like having

00:06:50.110 --> 00:06:52.570
half
of the human race open to me that had not

00:06:52.570 --> 00:06:54.360
been
open to me before.

00:06:54.360 --> 00:06:58.070
Now I believe in reincarnation
and I believe we've been men and women many

00:06:58.070 --> 00:06:59.070
times.

00:06:59.070 --> 00:07:00.629
So there's nothing foreign in that way.

00:07:00.629 --> 00:07:01.629
This was different.

00:07:01.629 --> 00:07:05.910
This was kind of opening almost into,
I don't want to say an archetypal dimension

00:07:05.910 --> 00:07:11.000
of womanhood,
but certainly to the collective life

00:07:11.000 --> 00:07:16.840
being lived by women in history, in time.

00:07:16.840 --> 00:07:20.900
So the joy was just to experience a whole
different way

00:07:20.900 --> 00:07:25.170
of being alive than I had known as Chris Bache.

00:07:25.170 --> 00:07:29.770
As the academic as the male engaging in academic
conversation.

00:07:29.770 --> 00:07:33.650
And here you're dealing with a very
different kind of connection and flow between

00:07:33.650 --> 00:07:34.650
women.

00:07:34.650 --> 00:07:35.849
Yeah, I thought that was fascinating.

00:07:35.849 --> 00:07:37.740
It's an interesting part of your book.

00:07:37.740 --> 00:07:41.280
I wish every
man could have an experience like this.

00:07:41.280 --> 00:07:44.110
It truly, it does change things profoundly.

00:07:44.110 --> 00:07:46.069
You know,
and the other way around and women should

00:07:46.069 --> 00:07:47.069
have the other.

00:07:47.069 --> 00:07:51.890
So we understand what each other is
contending with in our bodies in this reality.

00:07:51.890 --> 00:07:55.190
So let's move forward to session 11.

