That is it awakened the depth of
compassion in me, which I think was embedded

00:09:23.130 --> 00:09:26.980
at
a soul level to prepare me to take on the

00:09:26.980 --> 00:09:29.820
work,
which is something my soul had chosen to do

00:09:29.820 --> 00:09:31.900
in
this lifetime.

