What I learned was that just as
individual trauma gets buried in our individual

00:09:37.130 --> 00:09:45.290
psyche and can compromise our individual health,
the trauma of history is buried in the collective

00:09:45.290 --> 00:09:47.660
psyche of humanity.

00:09:47.660 --> 00:09:52.690
And so anything which is not
resolved by the species that any one generation

00:09:52.690 --> 00:09:58.000
accumulates in these massive memory structures
that I call metacoic systems.

