And what I think
was happening was that something guiding my

00:10:01.410 --> 00:10:06.420
sessions
began to use my sessions in order to confront,

00:10:06.420 --> 00:10:12.190
absorb and transmute vast territories of collective
anguish

00:10:12.190 --> 00:10:17.630
hat were embedded in the collective psyche,
